<style>
/* ═══════════════════════════════════════════
   PROTOCOLO R1 — LANDING PAGE STYLES
   Design: Dark theme, MaxFocos brand
   Palette: #0D0D0D, #1A1A1A, #FDE112, #FFF
   Typography: Neue Kaine (titles), Geist Mono (body)
